<p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 15px; color: #1c3f94;">Thank you for your interest in the Mass Solar Connect program.</p>
<p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 15px;">The Mass Solar Connect program has achieved unparalleled success as Direct Energy Solar contracted <strong>over 200 systems</strong>, far exceeding Mass Energy&rsquo;s program goal.</p>
<p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 15px;">Although the program has officially been closed by the Massachusetts Clean Energy Center, Direct Energy Solar is pleased to offer the reduced program pricing <span class="appleLinksGreen" style="color: #61af3f; font-weight: bold;">UNTIL SEPTEMBER 30</span> to all homeowners who signed up for a free solar consultation <span class="appleLinksGray">before August 31.</span></p>
<p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 15px;"><strong>Please contact your Solar Consultant to move forward or call us at 800-903-6130.</strong></p>
